{
  "book": "enos",
  "bookName": "Enos",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel the Nigerian"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 412.476,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then behold, I, Enos, knowing my father",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.734,
      "end": 4.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was a just man\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.772,
      "end": 6.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he taught me in his language,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 6.949,
      "end": 10.153,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in the nurture and admonition of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.333,
      "end": 12.794,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and blessed be the name of my God for it\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.474,
      "end": 16.725,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will tell you of the wrestle which I had before God,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 16.905,
      "end": 19.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before I received a remission of my sins.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.046,
      "end": 23.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I went to hunt beasts in the forests;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 23.198,
      "end": 26.588,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which I had often heard my father speak",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 26.768,
      "end": 28.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning eternal life",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 28.713,
      "end": 32.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the joy of the saints, sunk deep into my heart.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 32.876,
      "end": 34.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my soul hungered;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 34.542,
      "end": 36.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I kneeled down before my Maker,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 36.951,
      "end": 38.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to him",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 38.664,
      "end": 41.358,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mighty prayer and supplication for my own soul;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 41.538,
      "end": 43.814,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all the day long did I cry to him;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 43.994,
      "end": 45.944,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and when the night came",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 46.124,
      "end": 48.074,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did still raise my voice high",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 48.254,
      "end": 49.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it reached the heavens.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 50.606,
      "end": 53.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there came a voice to me, saying:",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 53.201,
      "end": 55.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Enos, your sins are forgiven you,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 55.889,
      "end": 57.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you shall be blessed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 58.148,
      "end": 60.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew that God could not lie;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 61.068,
      "end": 62.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, my guilt was swept away.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 63.606,
      "end": 65.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said: Lord, how is it done?",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 66.329,
      "end": 67.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 68.042,
      "end": 70.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Because of your faith in Christ,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 70.358,
      "end": 72.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom you have never before heard nor seen.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 73.046,
      "end": 74.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many years pass away",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 75.13,
      "end": 77.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before he shall manifest himself in the flesh;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 78.096,
      "end": 79.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, go,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 79.251,
      "end": 81.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "your faith has made you whole.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 81.696,
      "end": 83.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, when I had heard these words",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 84.105,
      "end": 88.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to feel a desire for the welfare of my brothers, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 89.115,
      "end": 92.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I poured out my whole soul to God for them.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 92.721,
      "end": 95.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while I was thus struggling in the spirit,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 95.92,
      "end": 99.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the voice of the Lord came into my mind again, saying:",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 99.676,
      "end": 101.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will visit your brothers",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 101.574,
      "end": 104.778,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to their diligence in keeping my commandments.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 104.958,
      "end": 107.187,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have given to them this land,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 107.367,
      "end": 109.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a holy land;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 109.312,
      "end": 110.984,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I curse it not",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 111.164,
      "end": 113.579,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except for the cause of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 113.759,
      "end": 117.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I will visit your brothers according as I have said;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 117.236,
      "end": 121.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their transgressions will I bring down with sorrow upon their own heads.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 122.374,
      "end": 125.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I, Enos, had heard these words,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 125.294,
      "end": 127.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my faith began to be unshaken in the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 128.168,
      "end": 133.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I prayed to him with many long strugglings for my brothers, the Lamanites.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 133.956,
      "end": 137.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had prayed and labored with all diligence,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 137.805,
      "end": 139.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 139.425,
      "end": 142.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will grant to you according to your desires,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 142.577,
      "end": 143.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of your faith.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 144.65,
      "end": 148.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, this was the desire which I desired of him\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 148.406,
      "end": 150.078,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if it should so be",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 150.258,
      "end": 152.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my people, the Nephites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 152.342,
      "end": 154.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should fall into transgression,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 154.658,
      "end": 156.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by any means be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 156.881,
      "end": 159.389,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamanites should not be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 159.569,
      "end": 164.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God would preserve a record of my people, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 165.136,
      "end": 168.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be by the power of his holy arm,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 168.288,
      "end": 172.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it might be brought forth at some future day to the Lamanites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 173.019,
      "end": 175.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that, perhaps, they might be brought to salvation\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 176.439,
      "end": 179.411,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For at the present our strugglings were vain",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 179.591,
      "end": 181.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in restoring them to the true faith.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 182.139,
      "end": 184.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they swore in their wrath that,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 184.409,
      "end": 185.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it were possible,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 186.168,
      "end": 188.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would destroy our records and us,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 188.995,
      "end": 191.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all the traditions of our fathers.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 192.322,
      "end": 193.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, I knowing",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 193.709,
      "end": 196.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God was able to preserve our records,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 197.0,
      "end": 200.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cried to him continually, for he had said to me:",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 200.291,
      "end": 202.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whatsoever thing you shall ask in faith,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 203.072,
      "end": 205.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that you shall receive in the name of Christ,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 206.131,
      "end": 207.803,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall receive it.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 208.483,
      "end": 209.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I had faith,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 210.103,
      "end": 211.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to God",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 211.955,
      "end": 213.998,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would preserve the records;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 214.178,
      "end": 215.896,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 216.076,
      "end": 220.348,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would bring them forth to the Lamanites in his own due time.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 221.028,
      "end": 225.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew it would be according to the covenant which he had made;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 225.713,
      "end": 227.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so my soul rested.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 228.018,
      "end": 229.643,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 229.823,
      "end": 232.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Your fathers have also required of me this thing;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 232.929,
      "end": 236.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall be done to them according to their faith;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 236.406,
      "end": 238.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for their faith was like to your.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 239.408,
      "end": 243.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Enos, went about among the people of Nephi,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 243.303,
      "end": 245.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying of things to come,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 245.666,
      "end": 249.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and testifying of the things which I had heard and seen.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 249.736,
      "end": 253.73,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record that the people of Nephi sought diligently",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 253.91,
      "end": 257.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to restore the Lamanites to the true faith in God.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 257.341,
      "end": 259.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But our labors were vain;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 259.564,
      "end": 261.189,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their hatred was fixed,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 261.369,
      "end": 263.737,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were led by their evil nature",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 263.917,
      "end": 269.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they became wild, and ferocious, and a blood-thirsty people,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 269.391,
      "end": 272.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of idolatry and filthiness;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 272.45,
      "end": 275.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeding upon beasts of prey; dwelling in tents,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 275.927,
      "end": 278.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and wandering about in the wilderness",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 278.986,
      "end": 283.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with a short skin belt about their waist and their heads shaven;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 283.299,
      "end": 287.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their skill was in the bow, and in the cimeter, and the ax.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 288.03,
      "end": 291.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many of them ate nothing save it was raw meat;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 291.461,
      "end": 294.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were continually seeking to destroy us.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 294.835,
      "end": 297.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the people of Nephi tilled the land,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 297.755,
      "end": 300.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and raise all manner of grain, and of fruit,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 300.489,
      "end": 302.022,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of herds,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 302.202,
      "end": 305.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of all manner of cattle of every kind,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 305.54,
      "end": 308.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goats, and wild goats, and also many horses.",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 309.657,
      "end": 312.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there were very many prophets among us.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 312.391,
      "end": 316.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people were a stiffnecked people, hard to understand.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 316.786,
      "end": 319.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was nothing save it was great harshness,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 320.077,
      "end": 325.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "preaching and prophesying of wars, and contentions, and destructions,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 325.18,
      "end": 327.595,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continually reminding them of death,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 327.775,
      "end": 329.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the duration of eternity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 330.091,
      "end": 332.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the judgments and the power of God,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 332.732,
      "end": 335.611,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all these things\u2014stirring them up continually",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 335.791,
      "end": 338.577,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to keep them in the fear of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 338.757,
      "end": 341.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say there was nothing short of these things,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 341.863,
      "end": 344.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and very great plainness of speech,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 344.272,
      "end": 347.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "would keep them from going down speedily to destruction.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 347.981,
      "end": 351.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner do I write concerning them.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 351.958,
      "end": 356.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw wars between the Nephites and Lamanites in the course of my days.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 357.421,
      "end": 359.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I began to be old,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 359.551,
      "end": 362.662,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and an hundred and seventy and nine years had passed away",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 362.842,
      "end": 366.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that our father Lehi left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 367.609,
      "end": 370.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that I must soon go down to my grave,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 370.761,
      "end": 373.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having been wrought upon by the power of God",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 373.913,
      "end": 376.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I must preach and prophesy to this people,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 377.065,
      "end": 380.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and declare the word according to the truth which is in Christ.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 380.589,
      "end": 382.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I have declared it in all my days,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 383.091,
      "end": 386.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have rejoiced in it above that of the world.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 386.79,
      "end": 389.112,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I soon go to the place of my rest,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 389.292,
      "end": 390.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is with my Redeemer;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 391.051,
      "end": 393.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that in him I shall rest.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 393.785,
      "end": 395.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I rejoice in the day",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 395.776,
      "end": 398.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when my mortal shall put on immortality,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 398.928,
      "end": 400.553,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall stand before him;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 400.733,
      "end": 403.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall I see his face with pleasure,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 403.235,
      "end": 404.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will say to me:",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 404.948,
      "end": 406.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Come to me, you blessed,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 406.8,
      "end": 410.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there is a place prepared for you in the mansions of my Father.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 410.927,
      "end": 411.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 150
    }
  ]
}